---
title: Prawn & Coconut Rice with Red Pepper, Coriander & Peanut Drizzle
description: From box to plate in just 35 minutes Chef Lizzie’s recipe is perfect for those on the go that want to eat balanced dishes. Not only that, this meal is packed full of flavour using lime, coriander, garlic and ginger to making this meal a win-win healthy, quick and full of flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/prawn-coconut-rice-9c8ec0e9-ea1225ef.jpg
